Defn.name: Description
Defn.val: The Renesas RA6T2 Group is the second RA ASSP product targeting for motor and inverter control solutions. The RA6T2 combines an Arm Cortex-M33 with a hardware accelerator for motor control and high-speed flash memory for high-speed real-time performance at 240MHz. It can also realize next-generation high-speed, high-response motor algorithms and improve parallel processing performance such as other communication processing.
